{"tid":958262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★天晉業主不滿管理費擬加一成 港鐵總部示威","createTime":"2018-12-27T16:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T06:22:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"e754be264ed89373d713d4e805c455083104a5c5","tid":958262,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yggeTpGeeffiMYssfHE5sQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/ec72e14e2bdcacd7ce741ec364cc4402\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyggeTpGeeffiMYssfHE5sQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fec72e14e2bdcacd7ce741ec364cc4402&h=e5ff5a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=EFWHbqjXg3nBn6j8Edq25DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f7e040d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】10多名將軍澳屋苑「天晉一期」的業主今午(27日)到港鐵總部示威，他們舉起多個寫「強烈抗議霸權加費」、「我們憤怒了」的標語，不滿管理公司港鐵無理大幅加管理費9.1%，要求港鐵凍結管理費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天晉住宅業主小組委員會主席黎兆聰表示，上月收到管理處通知因財赤加管理費，但曾擔任上屆業主委員會主席的他指出，截至今年9月屋苑的總財政盈餘錄得264萬港元，今年首9個月也錄得60萬港元盈餘，財政穩健，加上來年屋苑無重大維修工程，屋苑已購買物業保險，可賠償因山竹等天災意外造成的財務損失，質疑港鐵的加價理由牽強。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎指目前業主需繳付每呎4.3港元的管理費，按其800呎居所為例，每月管理費2600港元，若加價每月額外多付250港元，上月已收集120名業主簽名反對加管理費。他表明業主<span style=\"color: red;\">不排除發動集體罷交費的升級行動。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A9%E6%99%89%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%B2%BB%E6%93%AC%E5%8A%A0-%E6%88%90-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-085007520.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2599%2589%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-085007520.html&d=EFWHbqjXg3nBn6j8Edq25DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3ab3bb9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A9%E6%99%89%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%B2%BB%E6%93%AC%E5%8A%A0-%E6%88%90-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-085007520.html</a>"},{"pid":"08933c440500f40ecf6c9ae8de18da3bc5b7f04d","tid":958262,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9c403516a839031464ff2a90c2a452f125e978","tid":958262,"uid":98386,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:09:15.000Z","msg":"唔加你班仆街管理費馬屎坑份花紅點樣愈出愈多"},{"pid":"add9fa7fa99a193300bf3610f48ee349f5cdaf87","tid":958262,"uid":17646,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"正係罷交渣<br />\n換公司啦"},{"pid":"62cf80ff3486294234c7128ecb8846cfd3d55a7b","tid":958262,"uid":29093,"like":70,"dislike":5,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:22:18.000Z","msg":"依家啲廢中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錢買樓無錢交管理費"},{"pid":"b01467fe96b85f38cfedc9e32bda6613e8a0ac3e","tid":958262,"uid":15484,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"黎指目前業主需繳付每呎4.3港元的管理費，按其800呎居所為例，每月管理費2600港元<br />\n<br />\n計錯數？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221501828e68543f03d70b7107b0914afbc8adfa","tid":958262,"uid":14918,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:27:28.000Z","msg