理費9.1%，要求港鐵凍結管理費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天晉住宅業主小組委員會主席黎兆聰表示，上月收到管理處通知因財赤加管理費，但曾擔任上屆業主委員會主席的他指出，截至今年9月屋苑的總財政盈餘錄得264萬港元，今年首9個月也錄得60萬港元盈餘，財政穩健，加上來年屋苑無重大維修工程，屋苑已購買物業保險，可賠償因山竹等天災意外造成的財務損失，質疑港鐵的加價理由牽強。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎指目前業主需繳付每呎4.3港元的管理費，按其800呎居所為例，每月管理費2600港元，若加價每月額外多付250港元，上月已收集120名業主簽名反對加管理費。他表明業主<span style=\"color: red;\">不排除發動集體罷交費的升級行動。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A9%E6%99%89%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%B2%BB%E6%93%AC%E5%8A%A0-%E6%88%90-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-085007520.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2599%2589%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-085007520.html&d=EFWHbqjXg3nBn6j8Edq25DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3ab3bb9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A9%E6%99%89%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%B2%BB%E6%93%AC%E5%8A%A0-%E6%88%90-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-085007520.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:35:46.000Z","msg":"廢佬竟然&quot;佔領&quot;MTR<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b3fbca63cd5964eeb01a5a8d538e2b71c65bb4","tid":958262,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:37:55.000Z","msg":"ON9先住港鐵D樓<br />\n以前做港鐵物業維修,D料垃圾到"},{"pid":"e0fb94659e152c6968ea2568cc1d88dce3da3b51","tid":958262,"uid":14631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"793604399e6df50101b7d55f7ce5db4dd749e20c","tid":958262,"uid":124585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e754be264ed89373d713d4e805c455083104a5c5","tid":958262,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:05:41.